      "name": "PowerShell Reverse Shell Campaign via .lnk Phishing Lure (Eryx_cameo_details_.zip)",
      "description": "A malicious .lnk file distributed in a ZIP archive executes obfuscated PowerShell to download a reverse shell from GitHub. The shell connects to bulletproof-hosted C2 infrastructure on AS14956 (RouterHosting/FranTech/Cloudzy). Two GitHub accounts and two C2 IPs identified. Campaign active since December 2025.",
